Items.c: <[>這錢包就掉在賭場外,就算不是不義之財,也是誰準備繳給賭場的賭金,還不如讓我拿了。<]>
Items.mt: <[>This wallet was dropped outside the casino, and even if it wasn't ill-gotten gains, it was a bet that someone was going to pay to the casino, so I might as well take it. <]>
